&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Metric rib-scale 128                                                   <br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Metric version 64bit                                                   <br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;NSF-aware route hold timer is 240                                      <br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color:#d3d3d3">Router-ID: 6.6.6.6</span>                                                     <br />
