D&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10.1.11.0/24                                                                <br />
R4(config)#
</code></div>
<p>
On downstream routers, the default route can be verified using the command <code><b>show ip route</b></code>.
</p>

<div style="background-color:#f4f0ec; border-style:solid;border-width:1px;border-color:#D3D3D3">
<code>
R8#<b>show ip route | b Gate </b> <br />
