<p>
In named mode, the variance command can be configured under the topology base section of the appropriate address family.
</p>

<div style="background-color:#f4f0ec; border-style:solid;border-width:1px;border-color:#D3D3D3">
<code>
R8#<b>configure terminal</b>                                                      <br />                                          
