&nbsp;&nbsp;Outgoing update filter list for all interfaces is not set                        <br />                 
<span style="background-color:#d3d3d3">
&nbsp;&nbsp;Incoming update filter list for all interfaces is not set <br />                 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;GigabitEthernet0/0 filtered by (prefix-list) PL_DENY_1921681617 (per-user), default is not set           <br />                 
